# How to run

## Single machine instructions
### Starting Kafka services and the topic producer

- Start zookeeper and kafka, on a mac (assuming kafka installed using homebrew):
    -- `zkServer start`
    -- `kafka-server-start /usr/local/etc/kafka/server.properties`

- Create a topic
    -- `kafka-topics --create --zookeeper localhost:2181 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1 --topic madebar`

